{"type":"item.completed","item":{"id":"item_180","type":"agent_message","text":"The pattern is clear now: Akka is walking its own `reference.conf` and loading internal FQCNs reflectively during actor-system bootstrap. I’m extracting those config-backed class names so I can stop doing purely one-at-a-time guesses and patch the exact startup surface."}}
